        "content": "## üîç Logs & Traces Correlation\n\n1. **View logs with traces**: Click on `trace=...` in filtered logs to jump to Tempo trace\n2. **Explore raw data**: Use Raw JSON panel for debugging\n3. **Filter by severity**: Use Explore with query: `{exporter=\"OTLP\", service_name=\"hellgate\"} | json | severity=~\"SEVERITY_NUMBER_ERROR.*\"`\n\n## üìä Metrics\n- **Total Logs**: All logs in 5min window\n- **Warnings/Errors**: Severity-based counts (excludes app lifecycle noise)\n- **Rate Chart**: Real-time log rate by severity level"
